This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4750

Vim plugin to enhance the writing of human readable formats, such as Markdown.

This plugins sets auto paragraph formatting and convenient writing options to formats known to be read by humans, such as Markdown or Git commit message.

If you have any comments, fixes or requests, feel free to contact me or send me a patch.
The development also takes place at https://github.com/vivien/vim-addon-human
